CustomField.description: Defines an upper limit to the deduction amount that can be withheld on a per Pay Calendar Period basis. When deductions are calculated, the deduction amount withheld will be adjusted to ensure this amount is not exceeded. If blank no limit applies
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines an upper limit to the deduction amount that can be withheld on a per Pay Calendar Period basis. When deductions are calculated, the deduction amount withheld will be adjusted to ensure this amount is not exceeded. If blank no limit applies
CustomField.label: Pay Calendar Period Deduction Limit
